# Decisions Index

## Overview
This section records all significant decisions made during the development of The Kepler Testimonies, including community votes and creative choices.

## Decision Records

| ID | Date | Decision | Outcome |
|----|------|----------|---------|
| [001](001-premise-selection.md) | 2025-12 | Premise selection | THE KEPLER TESTIMONIES selected |
| [002](002-governance-adoption.md) | 2026-01 | Governance adoption | Formal governance framework implemented |
| [003](003-foundation-choices.md) | 2026-01-08 | Foundation choices | Stopover + Agreement Problem + Investigation structure |

## Decision Types

### Community Votes
Major narrative decisions put to the community via GitHub Discussions polls.

### Director Decisions
Tier 3 decisions made by jwynia, typically to break ties or resolve deadlocks.

### Creative Decisions
Choices made by the AI team during drafting that are significant enough to document.

### Technical Decisions
Choices about how the project operates, tools used, or process changes.

